import { Box, Card, CardBody, CheckboxIcon, Input, InputGroup, InputLeftElement, InputRightElement } from "@chakra-ui/react"

export default function Busqueda() {
    return (
        <Box position="relative" marginX={30}>
            <Card h="61vh" w="51vw" minWidth="205px" minHeight="360px" borderRadius="35px">
                <CardBody >
                    <InputGroup>
                        <InputLeftElement
                            pointerEvents='none'        
                            fontSize='1.2em'
                            children=''
                        />
                        <Input placeholder='Buscar canción' />
                    </InputGroup>
                </CardBody>
            </Card>
        </Box>
    );
}
